              üíº LinkedIn
            </a>
            <a href="https://www.facebook.com/syedbokharibsp" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="social-link">
              üìò Facebook
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="photo-card">
          <img
            src="/images/headshot.jpg"
            alt="Syed Bokhari - Registered NDIS Practitioner"
            loading="lazy"
          />
          <div class="photo-caption">
            <strong>Syed Bokhari</strong><br>
            <small>Registered Behaviour Support Practitioner</small>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="qualifications">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="h2 text-center">Academic Foundation</h2>
      <p class="text-center text-secondary mb-4">
        Rigorous educational background informing clinical practice.
