        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="practice-approach">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="h2 text-center">My Practice Philosophy</h2>
      <p class="text-center text-secondary mb-4">
        Grounding every intervention in human rights and clinical evidence.
      </p>
      
      

      <div class="approach-grid">
        <div class="approach-card">
          <div class="approach-icon">üë§</div>
          <h4>Person-Centred</h4>
          <p>The participant is at the heart of every decision, ensuring dignity and choice.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="approach-card">
          <div class="approach-icon">üß†</div>
          <h4>Trauma-Informed</h4>
          <p>Recognizing the impact of past experiences on current behavioural presentations.</p>
        </div>
        
